qas.question: Where are Million Dollar Minute and Family Feud based?
Where are Dancing with the Stars, MasterChef, and The Block filmed?
Neighbours, Kath & Kim, Winners and Losers, Offspring, and Underbelly are examples of what kind of media produced in Melbourne?
Which national news-based programs are based in Melbourne?

answers.text: The Project, Insiders and ABC News Breakfast

qas.question: Which city is known as the game show capital of Australia?

context: <a2_0>Television shows<a2_0/> are produced in Melbourne, most notably Neighbours, Kath & Kim, Winners and Losers, Offspring, Underbelly , House Husbands, Wentworth and Miss Fisher's Murder Mysteries, along with national news-based programs such as <a3_0>The Project, Insiders and ABC News Breakfast<a3_0/>. <a4_0>Melbourne<a4_0/> is also known as the game show capital of Australia; productions such as Million Dollar Minute, Millionaire Hot Seat and Family Feud are all based in <a0_0>Melbourne<a0_0/>. Reality television productions such as Dancing with the Stars, MasterChef, The Block and The Real Housewives of Melbourne are all filmed <a1_0>in and around Melbourne<a1_0/>.
